"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-04-06-paris-olympics-may-bring-bedbug-infestation-britain-20598543\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Bedbugs may be set to travel around Europe this summer as Europe gears up for the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Complaints to councils about bedbugs rose 23% last year to 14,587 asthe creatures infest furniture and bedding.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They can travel on suitcases and clothes, sparking fears travel across the continent thissummermay worsen the crisis.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James Logan, scientist and CEO of Arctech Innovation, toldthe I: 'This year is the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Logan_High_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6332570456366563e-15, \"text\": \"James Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Logan_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Logan_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998813109, \"rank\": 1.1890234244644015e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Big events like that mean people are travelling more than normal, so we might see more transportation of bedbugs.\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is also likely to be a continued increase in infestations in the UK this summer.'\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9180841288574895, \"rank\": 0.08922479418302284, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rate of infestations in the UK is also going up due to global warming.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9180841288574895, \"rank\": 0.08922479418302284, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Because of climate change we have warmer weather.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it is hotter, insects tend to breed quicker and survive being transported,' Mr Logan said.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.7562843817064866, \"rank\": 0.32209885926486587, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the callouts made last year, 8,864 were to homes in London, with research from Spotta showing infestations in hotel were up by 278% since 2021.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999524020506, \"rank\": 2.7908892302499375e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenneth F. Haynes, a professor of entomology,previously told Metro.co.uk: 'It is possible to pick up bed bugs from any place where there is an infestation.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.951469520875488e-14, \"text\": \"F.\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Reporter\"}, {\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_Haynes\", \"score\": 0.9525790938233232, \"rank\": 0.04466822096732129, \"text\": \"Haynes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_Haynes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_Haynes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may be more difficult for an infestation to get started in a bus or train, but it certainly has happened.'\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1278, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the NHS,signs of bedbugs in the home include:  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  Britain has inrecent months also seen a steep rise in bedbugs, with experts chalking it up to the creatures hiding in secondhand furniture and increased travel post-pandemic.\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9992372173521552, \"rank\": 0.0007633627270374778, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}, {\"begin\": 1373, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.024010116989347e-17, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank