p://dbpedia.org/resource/Cimex\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3722636408956437e-40, \"text\": \"Bedbugs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cimex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cimex\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They latch onto items such as luggage, clothing and second-hand furniture, and will be transported into your home that way.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To get the latest news from the capital visit Metro'sLondon news hub.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_Hub\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"news hub\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_Hub\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/News_Hub\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's how they can also end up on public transport or in public buildings such as cinemas, and unfortunately, how people can bring them home from holiday.'\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ANSES, agovernmentagency which assesses health risks,found that one in 10 French householdshad experienced bedbugs between 2017 and 2022.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With tourists expected to flock toFrance next year for the Olympics- and right now for Paris Fashion Week - officials are trying to stamp out the pests.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In its July report, the agency said: 'The upsurge in bed-bug infestations in recent years has been due in particular to the rise in travel and the increasing resistance of bed bugs to insecticides.'\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a bedbug infestation you should be calling pest control, but in the meantime here are some things you could try to keep the pests at bay.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's likely this will not eradicate them completely but it could help.\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:NHS  Get in touch with our news team by emailing us atwebnews@metro.co.uk.\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2921, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9993608704168107, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"metro.co.uk\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our news page.\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Major UK train station is getting a giant new Wetherspoons pub this summer  ArrowMORE:What I Own: We bought a house boat for \\u00a3125,000 and joined a mooring community in Bermondsey  ArrowMORE:Six teenagers on trial after transgender girl attacked at party  Stay on top of the headlines with daily email updates.\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 3303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3000, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9180841288574895, \"rank\": 0.08922479418302284, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3040, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wetherspoons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wetherspoons\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wetherspoons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wetherspoons\"}, {\"begin\": 3162, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermondsey\", \"score\": 0.9999987049076682, \"rank\": 1.294903679035035e-06, \"text\": \"Bermondsey\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermondsey\",